body:
Hi,
  Below is a reduced test from recent crash I reported on IVL_UVM. Hope this is small enough for developers to debug and fix.

Thanks
Srini

```verilog
`define IVL_UVM


package ivl_uvm_pkg;

class uvm_phase;
endclass : uvm_phase 

virtual class uvm_component;
  function new ();
  endfunction : new 

  virtual function void end_of_elaboration_phase(uvm_phase phase);
    uvm_info_counter ();
  endfunction : end_of_elaboration_phase
endclass : uvm_component

  function uvm_count_info();
    uvm_info_counter++;
  endfunction : uvm_count_info


int uvm_info_counter;
string log_id = "IVL_GO2UVM";

endpackage : ivl_uvm_pkg

module m;
  import ivl_uvm_pkg::*;

  uvm_component c_0;

  initial begin
    c_0 = new ("c_0");
  end

endmodule : m


```

```log
iverilog -DVW_IVLOG_GO2UVM -DIVL_UVM -g2012 -I../ -o vw_ivl_go2uvm.vvp  -f flist.class 2>&1 | tee go2uvm_comp.log 	
../ivl_uvm_sf.sv:14: internal error: Can't find task uvm_info_counter in class uvm_component
../ivl_uvm_sf.sv:14: error: Enable of unknown task ``uvm_info_counter''.
../ivl_uvm_sf.sv:14: error: Unable to elaborate statement in function end_of_elaboration_phase.
```

